local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["lambaste"]={"lambaste","[læm'beɪst]","[læm'best]","vt.痛打",'vt.痛打,痛骂|||=lambast','They lambasted the report as a gross distortion of the truth.','他们激烈批评该报告是严重歪曲事实。','And you can be sure that when the referee cheats our boys, I\'ll be ready to lambaste him.','而且你可以放心，如果裁判对孩子们不公平，我会公开斥责他。'}
